  "description": "A serene landscape featuring a calm body of water in the foreground, framed by a dense forest of evergreen trees. Beyond the forest, snow-capped mountains rise dramatically under a cloudy sky. The water reflects the cloudy sky and the surrounding trees, creating a sense of depth. The contrast between the dark forest, the bright snow, and the gray sky adds to the visual appeal. There is a small island visible to the right in the water.",
